OL,5,Csave lives
OL,7,FA mother who lost her son in an e-
OL,8,Fscooter accident has created a short
OL,9,Ffilm calling on the Government to
OL,10,Fintroduce tighter restrictions on the
OL,11,Fvehicles.
OL,13,FCarly Calland lost her 14-year-old son
OL,14,FJacob after the e-scooter he was
OL,15,Friding on the back of crashed into a
OL,16,Fcar in Baguley in Wythensawe on 19
OL,17,FMarch 2025.
OL,19,FJacob suffered a serious head injury
OL,20,Fand was quickly treated by paramedics
OL,21,Fwho had arrived via air ambulance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
