OL,7,FNeither Jacob or the driver of the
OL,8,Fscooter, who was also 14, were wearing
OL,9,Fa helmet at the time of the crash.
OL,11,FHis mother, Carly, said: "He was
OL,12,Falready in the back of the ambulance
OL,13,Fwhen I got there. It was breathtaking,
OL,14,Fit was a scene I'd never seen before.
OL,16,F"That split second has changed his
OL,17,Flife, my life, everybody's life around
OL,18,Fme - and I just needed it for them to
OL,19,Funderstand."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
