OL,7,FJacob was taken to Royal Manchester
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital, where he was kept
OL,9,Funder sedation on an intensive care
OL,10,Fward for eight days.
OL,12,FThroughout his treatment, Carly sent
OL,13,Fher son text messages in the hope that
OL,14,Fhe could read them when he woke up and
OL,15,Funderstand what had happened to him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
