OL,7,FThree days into his treatment, on
OL,8,FSaturday 22 March, she wrote: "Morning
OL,9,Fson... your numbers are looking good,
OL,10,Fyour sodium levels are a little high
OL,11,Fso they had to give you some medicine
OL,12,Fto correct them.
OL,14,F"You also ain't reacting to the light
OL,15,Fin your eyes but that's okay because
OL,16,Fyou are under a lot of sedation which
OL,17,Fis good for you as we need your brain
OL,18,Fto get better xxx
OL,20,F"But mums here right by your side I
OL,21,Flove you son xx"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
