OL,7,FOver the next few days Jacob's
OL,8,Fcondition got worse and he eventually
OL,9,Fcontracted sepsis and went into
OL,10,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,12,FAfter 20 minutes of resuscitation he
OL,13,Fstabilised, but the swelling to the
OL,14,Fbrain continued to get worse.
OL,16,FIn a text to Jacob, Carly said: "I had
OL,17,Fa feeling there was something wrong...
OL,18,FYou're so poorly it's so scary! Come
OL,19,Fon buddy mum can't lose you! Bring
OL,20,Fthose numbers down for me!!! I love
OL,21,Fyou."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
