OL,4,Caccident calls for tighter laws to
OL,5,Csave lives
OL,7,FOn Wednesday 26 March, doctors told
OL,8,FCarly there was nothing more they
OL,9,Fcould do for Jacob. He died at 5.18am
OL,10,Fon Thursday 27 March.
OL,12,FDescribing him, Carly said: "Jacob was
OL,13,Fvery funny, very quick witted... He
OL,14,Fwas a cheeky chappy but a very special
OL,15,Fboy."
OL,17,FSince Jacob's death Carly has been
OL,18,Fcampaigning for tighter restrictions
OL,19,Faround the use of e-scooters,
OL,20,Fespecially for those under the age of
OL,21,F18.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
