OL,4,Caccident calls for tighter laws to
OL,5,Csave lives
OL,7,FAs part of her campaign, she has set
OL,8,Fup an e-petition to make it mandatory
OL,9,Ffor all e-scooter drivers to wear
OL,10,Fhelmets, take out insurance, and not
OL,11,Fcarry passengers.
OL,13,FIn the UK, it is already illegal to
OL,14,Fride e-scooters on public roads,
OL,15,Fpavements, or cycle lanes. If caught,
OL,16,Fthe rider can be fined and have their
OL,17,Fscooter seized.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
