OL,7,FHowever since 2019, 49 people have
OL,8,Fdied while riding e-scooters and Carly
OL,9,Fsays tougher enforcement needs to be
OL,10,Fput in place.
OL,12,FShe said: "Anyone can purchase one.
OL,13,FThey just say that it's got to be on
OL,14,Fprivate land, which come on, no one's
OL,15,Fjust riding it around their back
OL,16,Fgarden or riding it on a private land.
OL,18,F"They're going to buy them scooters to
OL,19,Fuse. they don't even have to wear
OL,20,Fhelmets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
