OL,7,F"There's no repercussions to their
OL,8,Factions in what they do, you know? The
OL,9,Fpolice might stop them, take it off
OL,10,Fthem, but there's no repercussions to
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FCarly has taken part in a short film
OL,14,Fhighlighting the dangers of e-scooters.
OL,16,FAs well as calling on the Government
OL,17,Fto do more, Carly has also shared her
OL,18,Fstory through a short film about the
OL,19,Feight days
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
