OL,7,FShe said: "It is a hard watch. It's
OL,8,Fthe most painful thing I've ever have
OL,9,Fto do, but the impact it's had has
OL,10,Fmade it worth it."
OL,12,FThe 19-minute film charts the events
OL,13,Fleading up to Jacob's crash all the
OL,14,Fway through to his death eight days
OL,15,Flater through CCTV, videos of the
OL,16,Fscene, and the text messages Carly
OL,17,Fsent to her son.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
