OL,7,FThe film opens with Ring doorbell
OL,8,Ffootage of Jacob leaving his home.
OL,9,FJust 18 minutes later, Jacob was in an
OL,10,Fambulance.
OL,12,FCarly said: "That split second has
OL,13,Fchanged his life, my life, everybody's
OL,14,Flife around me - and I just needed it
OL,15,Ffor them to understand."
OL,17,F"The impact of the video has already
OL,18,Fstopped people getting on that
OL,19,Fscooter. If I can stop one more, and
OL,20,Fthen one more, and then one more life,
OL,21,Fhow powerful is that?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
