OL,5,Csave lives
OL,7,FThe scene of the crash, a busy
OL,8,Fjunction in Wythenshawe, is covered in
OL,9,Fflowers for Jacob and his family.
OL,11,FCarly said: "It's very painful,
OL,12,Fknowing this is where it happened. Why
OL,13,Fdid you get on that scooter? We
OL,14,Fwouldn't be stood here Jacob if you
OL,15,Fdidn't do that, and that's what I'm
OL,16,Ftrying to tell other children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
